{"tid":145520,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"贊唔贊成香港填海、開發郊區、移山發展多啲土地？","createTime":"2017-03-06T10:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T13:00:00.000Z","uid":21161,"like":18,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"704b05cbfabdbb3acd5a352557f9d42e58176176","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"香港有大約1100平方公里<br />\n但係已發展既土地只有大約20%<br />\n而呢20%既土地就容納左700幾萬人<br />\n對比新加坡我地香港發展到既土地其實少好多<br />\n<br />\n大家想唔想填海、開發部份郊區、移山<br />\n發展多啲土地<br />\n大約開發5-6成土地 咁已經多好多地用<br />\n<br />\n可能開發既成本好貴 <br />\n但係可以一勞永逸<br />\n之後拎個啲地黎起樓、起商業區咩都得啦<br />\n太家都唔想香港咁細冇野行架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反對"},{"pid":"ff227142f056c3daecba00f6b7391513df8d3adf","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ca0802b1e519a63e732e7038829a4034625b7e","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0293a909391e349dc2b0e3abac630461ee7056c9","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人支持？"},{"pid":"47a7f9710bc3a9160870b103c1df4f9596137949","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:21:25.000Z","msg":"或者反對既都可以講下點解反對"},{"pid":"2f40b6c0bfe8b987b75ab04e457778b2231399ba","tid":145520,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"只要係新加坡既政策我都贊成"},{"pid":"02d6046cb367268b457c09ec4cfc42f32e648cac","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只要係新加坡既政策我都贊成</blockquote><br />\nChing你真係好鐘意新加坡架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日見你講新加坡野<br />\n<br />\nBtw 新加坡填海多過香港好撚多"},{"pid":"7a1a2444ea28a87b7c501441921f5dcc799edef0","tid":145520,"uid":33609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"香港其實一路都唔係無地 <br />\n係hold住晒D 地 屯積居奇"},{"pid":"f0287e5ec17523af948d031a3112152af14f41fd","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港其實一路都唔係無地 <br />\n係hold住晒D 地 屯積居奇</blockquote><br />\n我知香港有地<br />\n但係發展多啲土 我覺得始終都冇壞<br />\n你都想香港大啲多野行啲架<br />\n同埋香港開發得兩成土地唔覺得太少咩"},{"pid":"0fe0c3935336c98e99294a206e10e47ff958f3bd","tid":145520,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港其實一路都唔係無地 <br />\n係hold住晒D 地 屯積居奇</blockquote><br />\n叫政府用撚晒自己屯個啲先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  地產佬又屯 政府又屯 又放啲廢人過黎 真係優才都算 放啲垃圾過黎 負擔愈黎愈大又話要開發郊區 <br />\n又縱容炒樓 個個hold幾層咁"},{"pid":"f2e771360daf664c8760b2529549c193b1b5d949","tid":145520,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"反對<br />\n一日唔cut150人填幾多海剷幾多郊公都唔夠班支那狗住"},{"pid":"70acefceebc8fa9cb9d9939f922c7cb5de8b3928","tid":145520,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"源頭減人"},{"pid":"527e08aadf47bca2a89bb07d9ec571acacca9156","tid":145520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反對<br />\n一日唔cut150人填幾多海剷幾多郊公都唔夠班支那狗住</blockquote><br />\n所以你反對既原因係因為150？<br />\n姐係如果冇呢個問題你可能會贊成發展多啲土地？"},{"pid":"b95b95d10d97211d57182734262156610ef04763","tid":145520,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"兩成當中一半係馬路<br />\n實際住戶只有7%"},{"pid":"00a7e8166d2b6544980d7c500110a4f4da128c27","tid":145520,"ui